data.description: Gracing a tranquil cul-de-sac, the home's position in the cul-de-sac not only provides a peaceful retreat from the main road but also enhances the sense of privacy and community. The home welcomes you into a generous living space that radiates a blend of sophistication and comfort. The living room's vaulted ceiling, complete with a fan, amplifies the open and airy ambiance. Adjacent to the living space, the dining area is perfectly situated for both casual meals and formal gatherings. The heart of the home is the kitchen, outfitted with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large island that doubles as a breakfast bar. Overlooking the dining nook, the kitchen's layout is designed for seamless entertaining and family engagement.Out back, the property features a sizable concrete patio, ideal for outdoor entertainment or quiet relaxation. It is complemented by a spacious lawn enclosed by a privacy fence, offering a blank canvas for your landscaping dreams. Strategically located for the commuter, this home is a short drive from major employers such as Tesla, Samsung (Parmer & Taylor campuses), and Dell, making it an excellent choice for professionals seeking a minimal commute. Residents of this community enjoy access to a large swimming pool complete with exhilarating water slides, a well-equipped workout gym for staying fit, and scenic hike & bike trails for outdoor adventures. Adding to the allure, an elementary school ensures educational convenience, and a public golf course within the community provides leisure and entertainment options right at your doorstep. With its blend of home comfort, location convenience, and community amenities, this property is not just a house, but a place to call home. Schedule your showing today!
